description: Bayern Munich’s financial position could thwart a move for Bayer Leverkusen star Florian Wirtz, but the club are hopeful Jamal Musiala will pen a new contract soon. title: Chelsea into Champions League quarter-finals with two games to spare
description: Chelsea reached the Women’s Champions League quarter-finals with two games to spare and stayed perfect under Sonia Bompastor with a 3-0 win over Celtic.
